k.\", \"from\": 1807, \"to\": 1963, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1807, \"end\": 1812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999999854481, \"rank\": 1.460224066763841e-11, \"text\": \"Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 1948, \"end\": 1952, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Association_of_Black_Journalists\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NABJ\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Association_of_Black_Journalists\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Association_of_Black_Journalists\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his phrase\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 1862}, {\"ngram\": \"Black jobs\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1874}, {\"ngram\": \"the term\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1902}, {\"ngram\": \"hisdisastrous appearance\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 1940}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking on stage, the former president told a roomful of Black journalists that immigrants are taking \\\"Black jobs.\\\"\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 2081, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"stage\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 1982}, {\"ngram\": \"the former president\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 2004}, {\"ngram\": \"Black journalists\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2040}, {\"ngram\": \"immigrants\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2056}, {\"ngram\": \"Black jobs\", \"from\": 2069, \"to\": 2079}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When asked to define what constitutes a Black job, he claimed: \\\"A Black job is anybody that has a job.\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2185, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a Black job\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2132}, {\"ngram\": \"A Black job\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2158}, {\"ngram\": \"anybody\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2169}, {\"ngram\": \"a job\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2184}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's what it is.\\\"\", \"from\": 2186, \"to\": 2205, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He also made scathing comments about Harris, the first Black and Asian-American vice president, wildly and falsely claiming that she \\\"happened to turn Black\\\" only recently.\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2379, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2272, \"end\": 2286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Americans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8121092976654695e-24, \"text\": \"Asian-American\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Americans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"scathing comments\", \"from\": 2220, \"to\": 2237}, {\"ngram\": \"Harris\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2250}, {\"ngram\": \"Black\", \"from\": 2358, \"to\": 2363}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not know she was Black until a number of years ago when she happened to turn Black and now she wants to be known as Black,\\\" he said, before asking: \\\"So I do not know - Is she Indian?\", \"from\": 2381, \"to\": 2570, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 2417, \"to\": 2425}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2434}, {\"ngram\": \"Black\", \"from\": 2465, \"to\": 2470}, {\"ngram\": \"Black\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2509}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or is she Black?\\\"\", \"from\": 2571, \"to\": 2588, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Trump has faced a swarm of backlash from Democrats, pundits and the wider public for theracially-charged remarks.\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2703, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2590, \"end\": 2595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999999854481, \"rank\": 1.460224066763841e-11, \"text\": \"Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"h